  "3183730": {
    "name": "Driveloop: Survivors",
    "steam_appid": 3183730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Driveloop</strong> 是一款高强度的3D生存类射击游戏，设定在后启示录城市中。体验紧张的战术驾驶和爆炸性战斗，升级并定制您的车辆，以应对无尽的敌人浪潮。穿梭于现实世界启发的危险环境中，每个转角都可能致命。唯有最快者能生存。准备好掌控方向盘了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/4cdd64adb3f0a6a1e36691f80b4755b4.avif?t=1770049488\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras_big/4cdd64adb3f0a6a1e36691f80b4755b4.avif?t=1770049488 width=800 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/9c50dd364a6dff85f19364136f14ba23.poster.avif?t=1770049488\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/9c50dd364a6dff85f19364136f14ba23.webm?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/9c50dd364a6dff85f19364136f14ba23.mp4?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >穿越混乱的战场，击溃源源不断的蒸汽朋克敌人。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漂移、撞击，并释放强大火力，体验战术驾驶和爆炸战斗的激烈结合。探索受现实大都会启发的衰败城市，每个街角都隐藏着危险。无论是冲入敌群，躲避攻击还是发起毁灭性打击，以风格迎接混乱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/6f553e261084159fb57f3b288b7fd1f1.poster.avif?t=1770049488\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/6f553e261084159fb57f3b288b7fd1f1.webm?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/6f553e261084159fb57f3b288b7fd1f1.mp4?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握漂移与撞击之术是生存的关键。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过精准的漂移保持速度，撞击敌人，开启新的攻击路径！在这快节奏的战场中，您的车辆既是致命武器，也是坚固盾牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/e8ed68730f1e3bc313cac1e2fe1df752.poster.avif?t=1770049488\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/e8ed68730f1e3bc313cac1e2fe1df752.webm?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/e8ed68730f1e3bc313cac1e2fe1df752.mp4?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用快速决策和战略性思考超越敌人。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募一支专业团队为您的爱车配备更强武器，收集零件解锁强大升级。建立有效协同，成为无可阻挡的战斗机器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/33d9b0b986ecf5fe0a08c12f4ca14636.poster.avif?t=1770049488\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/33d9b0b986ecf5fe0a08c12f4ca14636.webm?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/33d9b0b986ecf5fe0a08c12f4ca14636.mp4?t=1770049488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Driveloop带你进入现实启发的后启示录城市。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从柏林废墟到巴黎破败大道，每种环境带来独特挑战和复杂布局。每个转角都是战场，每次转弯都可能是最后一次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras/4cdd64adb3f0a6a1e36691f80b4755b4.avif?t=1770049488\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183730/extras_big/4cdd64adb3f0a6a1e36691f80b4755b4.avif?t=1770049488 width=800 height=115 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高强度战斗</strong>：漂移、撞击，击败无尽的蒸汽朋克敌人，享受混乱激战。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>终极车辆定制</strong>：使用强大武器、独特队员和策略技能来提升战斗力。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>后启示录城市景观</strong>：探索受经典城市启发的美丽废墟。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样敌人种类</strong>：从成群小兵到重装机械敌人，挑战各类敌人。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史诗级Boss战</strong>：与需要精确时间和策略能力的巨大Boss对决。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略进阶</strong>：每次升级和队员加入后，解锁协同效应，提升战力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 加泰罗尼亚语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
